From: Dmitry Eremin <dmitry.eremin@intel.com>
Date: Wed, 4 Nov 2015 13:40:00 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] staging: lustre: fix buffer overflow of string buffer
References: bnc#1012382
Patch-mainline: 4.4.177
Git-commit: 9563fe8a2de9db5eb087fe0e48ec335ee66f8f41

commit 9563fe8a2de9db5eb087fe0e48ec335ee66f8f41 upstream.

